<L>Its native pow'rs mo&s;t perfect, &s;he by this</L>
<L>Illumes the headlong impul&s;e of de&s;ire,</L>
<L>And &s;anctifies his choice. The generous glebe</L>
<L N="365">Who&s;e bo&s;om &s;miles with verdure, the clear tract</L>
<L>Of &s;treams delicious to the thir&s;ty &s;oul,</L>
<L>The bloom of nectar'd fruitage ripe to &s;en&s;e,</L>
<L>And every charm of animated things,</L>
